          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Defunding United Nations Act of 2017</b> </p> <p>This bill prohibits funds made available to any federal agency for FY2017 and subsequent fiscal years from being used to make U.S. voluntary contributions to the regular budget of the United Nations or any U.N. agency.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-01-04T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
